data.description:
This affordable historic 1909, house has 3 bedroom, 1 bath and is nestled in the heart of St Louis. It's classic architecture, and cozy vibes, makes this the perfect place to create lasting memories. Open concept living and dining provides ample space for entertaining friends and family. The large kitchen boasts plenty of natural light. Imagine sipping your morning coffee by one of many windows in
the bonus three season sun room. Three well-appointed upstairs bedrooms offer plenty of room to spread out. Step outside to your large back yard, perfect for gardening, grilling, fire pit parties or just enjoying the great outdoors, it's a perfect place to unwind. While out in back, check out that handy oversized garage. Great space for your auto, hobbies, or just extra storage. Cafes, shops, parks, the Greenway bike path and the Bevo Mill all just steps away. Don't miss out on this opportunity to make 4142 Taft your own. Schedule a showing today!
